#### [NEW] `system_narrative_outline_pirate_haven.txt`
Thay đổi so với ship version:
- Phases descriptions → sociological thay vì technical
- Hook: "bạn đặt chân lên hòn đảo..." thay vì "con tàu khổng lồ..."
- Anatomy: governance/economy/defense thay vì weapon/hull/cargo
- Dark Reality: violence/exploitation/slave trade thay vì pirate medicine
- End: modern ruins/site thay vì archaeological wreck discovery

#### [NEW] `system_narrative_write_pirate_haven.txt`  
- Phase-based writing: SOCIOLOGICAL lens thay vì TECHNICAL
- Hook rules: location visual + governance paradox
- Góc Khuất: dark underbelly thay vì pirate medicine
- End chapter: modern significance thay vì wreck archaeology
- Examples: governance mechanics thay vì cannon mechanics

#### [NEW] `system_narrative_audit_pirate_haven.txt`
- Audit checks: governance coverage thay vì anatomy specs
- Economy check: underground economy completeness

#### [NEW] `system_narrative_review_pirate_haven.txt`
- Dark Reality compliance: exploitation scene thay vì surgery scene
- Subject consistency: location/haven thay vì ship/vessel

